care shall be taken of any difference in the length units of both the instances of <express_ref linkend="elemental_geometric_shape:arm:Elemental_geometric_shape_arm.Geometric_coordinate_space"/>, as unit conversion may be required.
</note>

<note number="2">The mapping-table defines two interpretations for this ARM entity. The first one uses the MIM entity <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item"/> which uses the same principle to define the transformation as the <express_ref linkend="elemental_geometric_shape:arm:Elemental_geometric_shape_arm.Axis_placement_mapping"/> 
